text: Her cyð on þisan gewritu þæt þurstan geann þæs landes æt Wimbisc into <Christes> cyrcean for his sawle & for Leofware & for æþelgyðe þam hirede to fostre æfter þurstanes dæge & æfter æðelgyþe.
& ælcon geare an pund to fulre sutelunge þa hwile þe we libban.
& gelæste se hired æt Xpes cyrcean swa hwæder swa he wille þam hirede into sancte Augustine, þe twelf pund be getale oððe twa hida.

Þis syndon þa gewitnysse þæs cwydes, Eadwerd kyncg & Ælfgifu seo hlæfdige & Eadsige arcebiscop & Godwine eorl & Leofric eorl & Ælfwærd biscop on Lundene & Ælfwine biscop on Winceastre & Stigand preost & Eadwold preost & Leofcild scirgerefa & Osulf Fila & Ufic & Ælfwine Wulfredes sunu & Ælfric Wihtgares sunu & ealle þa þegenas on Eastsexan.
& beon heora menn frige æfter heora beira dæge.
& na stinge nan mann æfter heora dæge on þæt land buton se hired æt Xpes circean & yrfan hi swa hi wyrðe witan.
& þissera gewritu syndan þreo, an is æt <Christes> cyrcean, oþer æt sancte Augustine & þridde biþ mid heom sylfan.
